The Finance & Admin Business Analyst is essential to the ongoing profitable operations for one of the most globally recognized and respected companies in the world. By overseeing our financial activities, you will enable IBM to continue to bring to market ground-breaking innovations such as Artificial Intelligence, Cognitive Solutions, Cloud Infrastructure, and Blockchain technologies, to name a few. 
 
Your Role and Responsibilities 
To primarily answer incoming calls but to include responding to customer requests received via mail, voicemail, email, and fax from PepsiCo employees. Additional responsibilities will include: 
Process inbound calls to determine appropriate action required to satisfy the needs of the Customer, including external customers & internal business partners. 
Utilize AR technology tools to document customer requests, issue resolution/referrals for follow up to ensure proper handling of all inbound calls. 
Achieve individual and team objectives to include: 
Aux Variance 
Average Call Handle Time
 Calls per Staffed Hour 
Abandoned Calls
 First Call Resolution
 Quality 
Refer unresolved issues to the appropriate area, i.e., Cash/ Vendor Master/ Escalation Teams, via the JIRA 
Maintain an on-target or above average Quality Monitor score. 
Maintain complete and accurate documentation within JIRA 
Maintain an On Target or better Teamwork Assessment Rating 
Contribute toward team goals and objectives; including attendance & schedule adherence 
 
 
Required Technical and Professional Expertise 
 
High School diploma 
Highly effective interpersonal & communication skills in a fast paced-environment 
Knowledge of software & Pepsi applications, i.e., Oracle, SAP, and all supporting system 
Prior Customer Service and Call Center experience of 1-3 years; additional collection experience preferred 
Highly developed listening, analytical and problem-solving skills 
Excellent PC skills 
Customer Service Orientation; including clear, effective verbal and written communication with pleasant tone 
Broad-based Pepsi AR business knowledge 
Preferred Technical and Professional Expertise 
 
Bilingual capabilities a plus 
Ability to work a shift within operating hours 7am â€“ 7pm EST 
